Maybe they changed this on their second patch, but I can open no more than four item windows at one time.  When I try to open the fifth one, it overwrites the fourth one, sort of like how it used to, only you can have three other ones opened.<br>
<br>
I like being able to open more than one item window at one time.  It allows for easier comparison of up to four items at the same time.  Closing them can be a drag, but that's why you have the escape key.<br>
<br>
